               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410104-name-574" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410104-name-574" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410104-name-574" type="surname" value="DAVIES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410104-name-574" type="given" value="DANIEL"></interp>DANIEL DAVIES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a glass and china dealer, and live in Church-lane, Whitechapel. I was in my parlour on the 4th of January, about eight o'clock—I saw a hand remove a frame of cruets from the window—I ran out, and saw the prisoner running—I lost sight of him for a moment when he turned the corner, I then saw him again, and he threw them from him—the cruets were broken—here is the stand—the prisoner was brought back in about a minute—I am sure he is the person.</p>
